Hi tamaraws! My groupmates and I will be conducting a written interview as part of our assessment in the Journalism Principles and Practices subject. We are currently looking for alumni from the Batch 2025 graduates under the Institute of ITHM and IE. The questions will focus on the insights of attendees regarding the batch valedictory address speech

Your responses will be kept confidential and used only for academic purposes

Kindly pm me or Patricia Franco ❤️
